      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- about -->
  <div class="healthcare-about">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="inner">
        <div class="table">
          <div class="cell text">
            <div class="title trade_gothic_condensed_bold">Small but Mighty</div>
            <p>Not at all proteins are equal. See how Vidafuel is superior.</p>
